727490f-a.title: Queens: 81st Street - 21st Avenue
727490f-a.text:
North Beach Amusement Park, at 81st Street, north of
Twenty-first Avenue. At the right is the swimming pool.
Beyond it is a section of the Rapelye house. All buildings
in this area were mone bv November 1933.
May 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
